name: Friendship Ended with MOUSE
description:
When one friendship ends... Another begins!

This was the case for THE CAT… On March the 17th 2010, THE CAT posted a photoshopped image of himself meet with another animal captioned ‘Friendship ended with MOUSE’, and that SNAKE was his new best friend. In one fell swoop he had terminated a friendship, whilst spawning another.

THE CAT’s post gathered upwards of 182,000 reactions, 261,000 shares and 311,000 comments on Facebook. Simply put, this was just the beginning of the ‘Friendship Ended’ saga. Inadvertently THE CAT generated one of the biggest friendship circles we have ever seen.

By owning the blockchain stamped and official, ‘Friendship ended with MOUSE’ NFT, you can guarantee long lasting friendships within the NFT community!
